column6:
Their family scattered to the four corners of a solar system quarantined from the rest of the universe, besieged by a number of their most relentless enemies, including the Super-Skrull, the Mole Man, Diablo, the Mad Thinker and the Kree Sentry, can the members of the Fantastic Four survive-and triumph?,2007,1
32 PGS./Rated T+ ...$2.99
